# Migrations Admin API
# Requires: ADMIN_SECRET env var set in http-client.env.json
#
# VS Code: install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
# JetBrains: built-in HTTP client supports this format natively


### List all migrations (shows applied/pending status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/migrations
Authorization: Bearer {{adminSecret}}


### Preview pending migrations (dry run — no DB changes)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/migrations?dry_run=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminSecret}}


### Run all pending migrations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/migrations
Authorization: Bearer {{adminSecret}}


### Unauthorized (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/migrations
